</index> Sed cum omnia sunt paria[,] ruptura<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>ruptura fili</term>
</index> fit in loco propiore.</p>
<p xml:id="Ch4.p24">Experimenta ergo<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>experimentum nulli exceptioni subjacens</term>
</index> quae nulli exceptioni subjacent, et rem clare ostendunt sunt mechanica<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>experimentum mechanicum</term>
</index> ponderibus<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>pondus adhibitum</term>
</index> sive Elateriis connectentibus<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>elaterium connectens</term>
</index> adhibitis. Quae si favent sententiae<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>sententia</term>
</index> meae, hinc singulari constat exemplo,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>exemplum singulare</term>
</index> quantum intersit inter motum absolutum,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>motus absolutus</term>
</index> et respectivum.<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>motus respectivus</term>
</index>
</p>
<p xml:id="Ch4.p25">Idem ut confirmetur, hoc utamur experimento[:] in globum unum
              pendulum<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>globus pendulus</term>
</index>
<app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">quiescentem</lem>
<rdg wit="#L">
<note type="editorial">
<hi rendition="#i">erg. L</hi>
</note>
</rdg>
</app> alius argillaceus<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>globus argillaceus</term>
</index> demittatur aequalis, si motus respectivus<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>motus respectivus</term>
</index> hic nihil differt ab absoluto,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>motus absolutus</term>
</index> idem erit eventus<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>eventus</term>
</index> qui ambis in se invicem incurrentibus, nimirum quiescent ambo simul.</p>
<p xml:id="Ch4.p26">Casus<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>casus inanis</term>
</index>
<anchor xml:id="LH_37_05_001v_casusinanis_rltn-1"/>
 ut duo corpora dura<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>corpus durum</term>
</index> in vacuo<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>vacuum</term>
</index> concurrant,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>concursus in vacuo</term>
</index> est inanis, <app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">atque alienus a natura rerum.<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>casus alienus a natura rerum</term>
</index>
</lem>
<note type="lemma-abbrev">atque</note>
<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> impossibilis </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> alienus a natura rerum. <hi rendition="#i">L</hi>
</rdg>
</app> Nam semper in omni incursu<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>incursus</term>
</index> cessio<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>cessio</term>
</index> est et restitutio<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>restitutio</term>
</index> etsi ea saepe a nobis non sentiantur, cum spongiosa corpora<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>corpus spongiosum</term>
</index> sunt, et motus per partes dispergitur.<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>motus per partes dispersus</term>
</index> Quoties vero non dispergitur, sed integer<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>motus integer</term>
</index> apparet <pb type="L"/>
<app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">motus[,] apparet praeclarum illud principium,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>principium naturae</term>
</index>
</lem>
<note type="lemma-abbrev">motus</note>
<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> verissima est </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> apparet praeclarum illud <app>
<rdg wit="#L" n="a">naturae p </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="b">Metaph </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="c">principium, <hi rendition="#i">L</hi>
</rdg>
</app>
</rdg>
</app> Conatum naturae<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>conatus naturae</term>
</index>
<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>natura</term>
</index> semper irresistibilem esse.<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>conatus irresistibilis</term>
</index> Semper centrum gravitatis mobilium<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>centrum gravitatis mobilis</term>
</index> in eadem recta procedet.<anchor xml:id="LH_37_05_001v_casusinanis_rltn-2"/>
</p>
<p xml:id="Ch4.p27">
<app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">Quoties major</lem>
<note type="lemma-abbrev">Quoties</note>
<rdg wit="#L">
<note type="editorial">|</note> deinde <hi rendition="#i">streicht</hi>  major <hi rendition="#i">L</hi>
</rdg>
</app> est firmitas corporis<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>firmitas corporis</term>
</index> quam ictus,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>ictus</term>
</index> totum propellitur. Si quis totam rerum machinam<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>machina rerum</term>
</index> tamen intueretur, videret corpus hoc<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>corpus cedens</term>
</index> quod cedit totum[,] considerandum ut alterjus partem in quo et restitutio
              est,<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>restitutio insensibilis</term>
</index> sed quae in nostro hoc corpore non est sensibilis, cum per tot alia
              distribuatur.<index indexName="Sachen">
<term>restitutio distributa</term>
</index>
</p>
